{"tid":1462117,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[佛教黃允畋] 教畜鼓吹謀殺示威者 呢單野竟然無人理？","createTime":"2019-08-13T10:01:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T14:06:29.000Z","uid":52658,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b05fa70715e8d853b99d31bccbea26b04eedb0b5","tid":1462117,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:01:30.000Z","msg":"屌你老母啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幫幫手 腥信去塞爆佛聯會個mail box啦<br />\n下面呢封信唔係我打 我借其他巴打<br />\n<br />\n佛教黃允畋電話：<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><strong>2605 8369</strong></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">info@bwwtc.edu.hk</span><br />\n<br />\nDear Principal Yip : <br />\n<br />\nI'm writing to lodge a complaint against one of your teachers 趙崇威 who spread hate speech on social media <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/1Zinp7u.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1Zinp7u.jpg&d=HBLsGxwPt4tNlCAdiZVEvktjIx4W8g%2FGk507jgkcous%3D&h=1eab92d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/1Zinp7u.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/8EL847v.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8EL847v.jpg&d=HBLsGxwPt4tNlCAdiZVEvktjIx4W8g%2FGk507jgkcous%3D&h=906d9744\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/8EL847v.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\nA teacher is a figure which many students look up to. Spreading hate speech on social media is neither a responsible nor ethical act. I believe an investigation into whether Chiu is professionally fit to carry out his teaching duties should be in place. The last thing we would want to see is our students being manipulated into spreading hate against each other.<br />\n<br />\nI'm also keeping the Hong Kong Professional Teachers' Union informed of my grave concerns. Your written reply is highly appreciated. <br />\n<br />\nThank you very much<br />\nA Hong Kong citizen<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">info@bwwtc.edu.hk</span><br />\n<br />\n有關貴校趙崇威老師於網上散播仇恨及殺人言論<br />\n<br />\n敬啓者,<br />\n<br />\n近日基於社會動盪, 市民大眾一般於網上社交媒體發表有關個人就事件之意見, 此舉無可厚非亦表現出香港社會言論自由之可貴。<br />\n<br />\n然 貴校趙崇威老師就有關事件於其社交媒體所發表之言論實在令人齒冷。作為教育學生之身份, 因著個人政治立場而說出「爆眼不足夠...烏合之眾死有餘辜。是學生亦不值可憐」此等語句<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/1Zinp7u.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1Zinp7u.jpg&d=HBLsGxwPt4tNlCAdiZVEvktjIx4W8g%2FGk507jgkcous%3D&h=1eab92d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/1Zinp7u.jpg</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/8EL847v.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8EL847v.jpg&d=HBLsGxwPt4tNlCAdiZVEvktjIx4W8g%2FGk507jgkcous%3D&h=906d9744\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/8EL847v.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n令人懷疑趙崇威老師作為教育者身份對學生關愛之心態是否有所扭曲。<br />\n<br />\n此次致函乃希望貴校就趙崇威老師之言論作出回覆如何處理, 相信作為佛教辦學團體學校, 絕對希望對學生以致社會上之弱勢階層表現關愛同理之感情。再次重申, 趙崇威老師之言論與校訓「明智顯悲」相違, 更令人擔憂其能否足以擔當教育者之身份。如貴校未能作出回覆, 有關資料將交予各大媒體作出跟進。"},{"pid":"754f15d0d58ace79755cd43b35fe74b299fe3269","tid":1462117,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:04:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f4e00466c0edc02c75e06849209ae0141a258ae","tid":1462117,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:05:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d27350d54c763df985f42823f7bb87a35049d05b","tid":1462117,"uid":254188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:08:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"26ad74f0d2cf7b2ad429d8090d6cee23db17158c","tid":1462117,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:22:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c17d9b12f96182fe330b994a0ad9c1c461b9067","tid":1462117,"uid":4640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:30:16.000Z","msg":"P